Who Do You Think You Are? Australia - Series 6, Episode 7




Lisa McCune

Actor Lisa McCune's career has flourished both on screen and stage. But the McCune family name she's made famous does not feature in her biological family tree. Lisa has learned that the man she grew up knowing as her grandfather is not actually her paternal grandfather.




Original Air Date: 19-Aug-2014
